sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Website as AI-Solutions Website
    participant API as Backend API
    participant Database as MongoDB Database
    actor Admin

    User->>Website: Open website
    Website->>API: Request published content
    API->>Database: Fetch services, projects, articles, events, gallery and testimonials
    Database-->>API: Return published content
    API-->>Website: Send website content
    Website-->>User: Display public pages

    User->>Website: Submit inquiry / review / chat message
    Website->>API: Send user details
    API->>API: Validate submitted data
    API->>Database: Save user record
    Database-->>API: Record saved
    API-->>Website: Send success response
    Website-->>User: Show confirmation message

    Admin->>Website: Login to admin panel
    Website->>API: Send login credentials
    API->>Database: Check admin account
    Database-->>API: Return admin data
    API-->>Website: Send login token
    Website-->>Admin: Open admin dashboard

    Admin->>Website: View dashboard and manage records
    Website->>API: Request inquiries, content and chats
    API->>Database: Fetch admin records
    Database-->>API: Return records
    API-->>Website: Send dashboard data
    Website-->>Admin: Display inquiries and content

    Admin->>Website: Update inquiry, content or chat status
    Website->>API: Send update request
    API->>Database: Save updated data
    Database-->>API: Update complete
    API-->>Website: Confirm update
    Website-->>Admin: Show updated result
